~ The Salty Dog menu ~

The Special: Deep Fried Flounder 2 Ducal Pieces
Caught this morning and fried to a crisp, served with a warm Skull Ale and Tartar Sauce, this succulent fish is sure to make your hunger pirates walk the plank!

Catch of the Year: Broiled Spicy Greenfish 5 Ducal Pieces
A Benzorite favorite! Locally farmed, our broiled Greenfish is seasoned with herbs and spices imported directly from Bria's Fay. Those halflings sure do have the best ingredients to make your tounge dance and your nostrils flare! Served with warm Skull Ale and a green salad. Tartar sauce available on request.

Seafood Platter 10 Ducal Pieces
Three helpings of Greenfish, two slabs of Deep Fried Flounder, 13 jumbo Abizian Shrimp, the Terror of Tyranny West Benzorite Crabcakes, all the Skull Ale you can drink, and a slice of lemon for only 10 gold pieces! It's a steal, but don't tell Tucker!

Skull Ale 1 Ducal Piece
Try the most famous local drink for a single gold piece! Not responsible for picked pockets and lost items as you throw up your Greenfish and Flounder into the Sea.

Merchant Tills
In Nordock Rogue and Bard characters may attempt to use Slight of Hand to steal a few coins from a vendor's purse. Simply click on this object and follow the conversation. However no reward comes without risk so note that there is a small chance of getting caught each time you try and as an illegal act if caught you face potential jail time from the guards. But a canny escape artist should be out in no time. Characters wishing to become more proficient at this should train in picking pockets. Success can only be met at each till once per reset and if discovered you cannot attempt on the same till again that reset.
A hollowed out skull containing a dark and somewhat strong smelling liquid. It's the specialty drink at the Salty Dog Tavern.

Greenfish are abundant in the seas that lap the coast of Nordock. While bland themselves, a concoction of pepper and other spices brings out a surprisingly tangy and pleasant flavor. This fish counts as a single food serving for resting purposes.
